Package: hp
Title: Pipe a function into help()
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Eric",
           family = "Leung",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "erictleung@outlook.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8724-1872"))
Description: After using autocomplete on a function, instead of scrolling
    to the front of the function to use the question mark to access the
    help page, this package allows you to pipe the function into a wrapper
    help function for easier access.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
